n, particularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/116537/', '', 'Felodipine, Amlodipine, Verapamil', 'Liraglutide, Lixisenatide', 1767369485);
